These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: indian, indonesian, dutch, french
1. Nationality:indonesian is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:french is between Nationality:indian and Nationality:indonesian##2
3. Nationality:french is on the right of Nationality:indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | indian | french | indonesian | dutch |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Food: grapes, pepper, watermelon, peach
1. Food:grapes is on the left of Food:peach##1
2. Food:pepper is in an odd position##4
3. Food:pepper is on the left or right of Food:grapes##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | pepper | grapes | peach | watermelon |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
Movie-Genre: crime, animation, action, scientific
1. Movie-Genre:scientific is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:crime##3
2. Movie-Genre:crime is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:action is between Movie-Genre:scientific and Movie-Genre:animation##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | scientific | action | animation |

 #################################
 
