.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Food: plum, watermelon, apple, mango
1. Food:watermelon == Food:watermelon##1
2. Food:mango is on the left or right of Food:apple##3
3. Food:apple is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:plum is in an even position##4
5. Food:mango is on the left of Food:watermelon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | apple | mango | watermelon | plum |

